---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
import { siteInfo } from "../../config/siteInfo";
---

<Layout
    title="Privacy Policy – Gehringer Consulting"
    description="Privacy policy and protection of personal data of Gehringer Consulting."
>
    <Header slot="header" />
    <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 py-16 text-gray-700">
        <h1 class="font-logo text-5xl text-center text-gray-900 mb-12">
            Privacy Policy
        </h1>

        <!-- Introduction -->
        <p
            class="text-center text-gray-600 mb-12 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed"
        >
            This privacy policy describes the way <strong
                >Gehringer Consulting</strong
            >
            processes personal information collected via this website, in compliance
            with the <strong>General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR)</strong>.
        </p>

        <!-- 1. Data Controller -->
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">1. Data Controller</h2>
        <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            The data controller is:
            <br />
            <strong>Philippe Gehringer</strong> — Gehringer Consulting
            <br />
            Email : <a
                href={`mailto:${siteInfo.email}`}
                class="underline hover:text-slate-900 transition"
                >{siteInfo.email}</a
            >
        </p>

        <!-- 2. Data Collected -->
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">2. Data Collected</h2>
        <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            The website <strong>gehringer.fr</strong> only collects personal data
            in the following cases:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-8 space-y-2">
            <li>
                When you use the <strong>contact form</strong> (name, email address,
                message);
            </li>
            <li>
                When you voluntarily communicate your information by email or
                via LinkedIn.
            </li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            No sensitive data (ethnic origin, political opinions, health, etc.)
            is collected.
        </p>

        <!-- 3. Purpose of Processing -->
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">3. Purpose of Processing</h2>
        <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">The collected data is used only to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-8 space-y-2">
            <li>Respond to your requests via the contact form;</li>
            <li>Contact you for professional proposals or exchanges;</li>
            <li>
                Ensure the administrative follow-up of your requests if
                applicable.
            </li>
        </ul>

        <!-- 4. Legal Basis -->
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">4. Legal Basis</h2>
        <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            The processing is based on your <strong>explicit consent</strong>,
            given when you submit the form or send a message voluntarily.
        </p>

        <!-- 5. Retention Period -->
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">5. Retention Period</h2>
        <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            Data transmitted via the contact form is kept for a maximum duration
            of
            <strong>12 months</strong>, then automatically deleted, unless a
            prolonged contractual relationship is established.
        </p>

        <!-- 6. Data Sharing -->
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">6. Data Sharing and Hosting</h2>
        <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            No data is shared or sold to third parties. Forms are hosted and
            processed via the <strong>Netlify</strong> platform, which applies GDPR-compliant
            measures for form management.
        </p>

        <!-- 7. User Rights -->
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">7. Your Rights</h2>
        <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            In accordance with the GDPR, you have the following rights:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-8 space-y-2">
            <li>Right of access to your data;</li>
            <li>Right of rectification or deletion;</li>
            <li>Right to object or limit processing.</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            You can exercise these rights by sending a message to:
            <a
                href={`mailto:${siteInfo.email}`}
                class="underline hover:text-slate-900 transition"
                >{siteInfo.email}</a
            >.
        </p>

        <!-- 8. Data Security -->
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">8. Data Security</h2>
        <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            Technical and organizational measures are implemented to protect
            your data against unauthorized access, loss, or modification.
        </p>

        <!-- 9. Cookies -->
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">9. Cookies</h2>
        <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            The website <strong>gehringer.fr</strong> does not place any tracking
            or advertising cookies. Only strictly necessary cookies for the operation
            of the site may be used (e.g., related to hosting or security).
        </p>

        <!-- 10. Contact -->
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-3">10. Contact</h2>
        <p class="mb-8 leading-relaxed">
            For any questions relating to privacy or your personal data, you can
            write to:
            <a
                href={`mailto:${siteInfo.email}`}
                class="underline hover:text-slate-900 transition"
                >{siteInfo.email}</a
            >.
        </p>

        <!-- Back Button -->
        <div class="text-center mt-16">
            <a
                href="/en"
                class="inline-block bg-gray-900 text-white px-8 py-3 rounded-xl hover:bg-gray-700 transition"
            >
                Back to Home
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>
    <Footer slot="footer" />
</Layout>
